name: Galactic Guardian: A 19th-Century Tale of the Future in Oil

prompt.prompt: Full body portrait of a futuristic riot police robot astride an extraterrestrial deer-like creature, set against a backdrop of an alien fortress. The image should represent the stylistic elements of late 19th-century Romanticism with a focus on atmospheric effects, intricate detailing, and narrative storytelling, primarily executed in oil, like the works of artists before 1912.
